---
import ContentPageLayout from "../layouts/ContentPageLayout.astro";

const tocItems = [
  { id: "where-we-come-from", label: "Where We Come From" },
  { id: "leadership-and-direction", label: "Leadership &amp; Direction" },
  { id: "what-kind-of-business-we-are", label: "What Kind of Business We Are" },
  { id: "how-we-approach-work", label: "How We Approach Work" },
  { id: "backed-by-containerking", label: "Backed by ContainerKing&reg;" },
  { id: "who-we-work-with", label: "Who We Work With" },
  { id: "where-we-operate", label: "Where We Operate" },
];
---

<ContentPageLayout
  metaTitle="ISOv8® | About Us"
  description="About ISOv8® — a UK business delivering shipping container conversions and steel anti-vandal buildings with a focus on clarity, specification, and long-term performance."
  keywords={["about ISOv8", "container conversion company UK", "steel anti-vandal buildings UK", "container conversions Lincolnshire", "portable buildings Scunthorpe"]}
  breadcrumbName="About Us"
  h1="About Us"
  tocItems={tocItems}
>
  <p class="text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    ISOv8&reg; operates as a sub brand and part of ContainerKing&reg; Limited, a UK registered business established through over 30 years of hands-on work in shipping containers, anti-vandal and portable buildings, and specialist fabrication.
  </p>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    ISOv8&reg; is not a new venture or a rebranded offer.
  </p>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    ISOv8&reg; exists to focus specifically on shipping container conversions and steel anti-vandal buildings supply to customers where specification, build quality, and long-term performance matter.
  </p>

  <h2 id="where-we-come-from" class="mt-14 scroll-mt-36 text-[2.25rem] font-[600] leading-tight text-black">Where We Come From</h2>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    ContainerKing&reg; has been built from the ground up &mdash; supplying, modifying, and delivering container and anti-vandal building solutions across a wide range of industries.
  </p>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    That experience is practical, not theoretical.
  </p>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    It comes from:
  </p>
  <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    <li>designing and building units that are used daily</li>
    <li>resolving real-world problems</li>
    <li>and understanding how these structures perform over time</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    ISOv8&reg; applies that experience to projects where detail, specification, and correct decision-making at the outset are critical.
  </p>

  <h2 id="leadership-and-direction" class="mt-14 scroll-mt-36 text-[2.25rem] font-[600] leading-tight text-black">Leadership &amp; Direction</h2>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    ISOv8&reg; is led by Steve Empson, Managing Director of ContainerKing&reg; Limited.
  </p>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    The business has been shaped through long-term commercial experience, including both successful growth and periods of significant challenge. Years of learning and our background has formed my views on how a proper business should operate and also how the correct decisions should be made &mdash; with a focus on structure, clarity, and long-term outcome rather than short-term gain.
  </p>

  <h2 id="what-kind-of-business-we-are" class="mt-14 scroll-mt-36 text-[2.25rem] font-[600] leading-tight text-black">What Kind of Business We Are</h2>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    We are a build-led business.
  </p>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    We are not sales-driven, and we are not structured around volume.
  </p>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    Our focus is on:
  </p>
  <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    <li>defining requirements properly</li>
    <li>specifying correctly</li>
    <li>and delivering work that performs as intended</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    Our approach (we appreciate) may not suit every customer or project.
  </p>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    It is designed for clients who value:
  </p>
  <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    <li>clarity before commitment</li>
    <li>realistic specification</li>
    <li>and outcomes that stand up over time</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="how-we-approach-work" class="mt-14 scroll-mt-36 text-[2.25rem] font-[600] leading-tight text-black">How We Approach Work</h2>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    Most problems in this sector originate before fabrication begins.
  </p>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    We focus on:
  </p>
  <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    <li>understanding the requirement in detail</li>
    <li>identifying constraints early</li>
    <li>and ensuring the proposed solution is appropriate</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    That often means:
  </p>
  <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    <li>asking direct questions</li>
    <li>challenging assumptions</li>
    <li>and occasionally advising against a proposed route</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    The objective is simple &mdash; get it right before it is built.
  </p>

  <h2 id="backed-by-containerking" class="mt-14 scroll-mt-36 text-[2.25rem] font-[600] leading-tight text-black">Backed by ContainerKing&reg;</h2>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    ISOv8&reg; operates within ContainerKing&reg; Limited, with full access to:
  </p>
  <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    <li>fabrication facilities</li>
    <li>experienced trades and engineers</li>
    <li>container supply and modification capability</li>
    <li>delivery and installation infrastructure</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    This provides full control from concept through to completion.
  </p>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    One team. One build. One point of responsibility.
  </p>

  <h2 id="who-we-work-with" class="mt-14 scroll-mt-36 text-[2.25rem] font-[600] leading-tight text-black">Who We Work With</h2>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    We work with commercially aware customers who need reliable, correctly specified space, including:
  </p>
  <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    <li>business owners and operators</li>
    <li>engineers and manufacturers</li>
    <li>contractors and infrastructure providers</li>
    <li>local authorities and commercial organisations</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    We are best suited to projects where:
  </p>
  <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    <li>decisions are considered</li>
    <li>quality is prioritised</li>
    <li>and long-term value matters</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="where-we-operate" class="mt-14 scroll-mt-36 text-[2.25rem] font-[600] leading-tight text-black">Where We Operate</h2>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    ISOv8&reg; operates from Scunthorpe, North Lincolnshire, delivering shipping container conversions and steel anti-vandal buildings across Lincolnshire, Yorkshire &amp; Humberside, the Midlands, and throughout the UK.
  </p>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    From our North Lincolnshire base, we supply and deliver bespoke container conversions and steel anti-vandal buildings to businesses, contractors, and organisations across:
  </p>
  <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    <li>Lincolnshire &mdash; including Scunthorpe, Lincoln, and surrounding areas</li>
    <li>Yorkshire &amp; Humberside &mdash; including Hull, Doncaster, Sheffield, and Leeds</li>
    <li>The Midlands &mdash; including Nottingham, Derby, Leicester, and wider regions</li>
    <li>Nationwide UK coverage for commercial and specialist projects</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[1.125rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#4b5563]">
    All units are built in-house and delivered using experienced HIAB hauliers, with clear guidance provided on site access, positioning, and installation to ensure a controlled and reliable delivery process.
  </p>
</ContentPageLayout>
